<p>This is an example of layout built using <a href="https://bootswatch.com/lux/">bootstrap lux</a></p>

<p>To use it as your default theme youâ€™ve to change layout configuration in your _config.yml, for example:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>defaults:
 -
    scope:
      path: ""
    values:
      layout: "git-wiki-bs-lux"
 -
    scope:
      path: ""
      type: "pages"
    values:
      layout: "git-wiki-bs-lux"
</code></pre></div></div>

